metadata.name: Supercars on Monument Circle
metadata.description: Utilizing 33 INDYCARS provided by the INDY RACING EXPERIENCE the SUPER BOWL 46 COMMITTEE arranged for 32 cars to be branded in the NFL teams colors and logos and ONE SUPER BOWL 46 branded car. The cars were placed in downtown INDIANAPOLIS in front of the monument on the circle. Photographer JASON LAVENGOOD took this iconic picture just after the cars had been put into position and prior to the thousands of people that would surround the cars while they were on display. This will be the ONLY DROP of this picture!
